headline: COMM Completes Strategic Divestiture for Core Focus: Stock to Gain?
summary: CommScope completed divestiture of Outdoor Wireless Networks (OWN) and Distributed Antenna Systems (DAS) businesses to Amphenol.

headline: Keysight Announces Date of First Quarter 2025 Financial Results Conference Call
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., February 04, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) will release financial results for the fiscal quarter ending January 31, 2025 after the close of the market on Tuesday, February 25, 2025. The company will host a conference call that day at 1:30 p.m. PT (4:30 p.m. ET) to review the financial results.
